	)
	(text "By the time of FrontBuffer~{BackBuffer} switching value, \nthe memory/video bus would be stoped for ~15us -> no clock sync required.\nAnd wont be used after frontPorch isn't triggered."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 313.69 107.95 0)
		(effects
